title: Axiom's Johnson Sees Oil Price Lower, More Supply Coming(Audio)

description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Gordon Johnson, Head of Alternative Energy, Metals & Mining & Equip and Managing Director at Axiom Capital Management, on oil and what's been driving the commodity stock rally.
